div1.p: IN THE UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT OF THE WESTERN DISTRICT OF WASHINGTON NORTHERN DIVISION.
In the Matter of the Petition of FRANCIS STEPHEN MEDCRAF for Writ of Habeas Corpus. No.3038.

Comes now the respondent and moves the court to quash the writ heretofore issued in the above entitled cause and to dismiss the above entitled proceeding and to remand the petitioner FRANCIS STEPHEN MEDCRAF to the custody of Robert T. Hodge, Sheriff of King County, Washington.
This motion is based upon the record and pleadings herein.
Dated at Seattle, Washington, this 28th day of June, 1915.
div1.ab: Alfred H Lundin By Frank P Helsell Attorneys for Respondent.
